## AI Coding Rules (Cursor)

### Stack: {{stack}}

- **Build**: `npm run dev` (Vite), `npm run build` (vue-tsc + vite build)
- **Test**: `npm test` (vitest + @vue/test-utils)
- **Structure**: Composition API only — always `<script setup lang="ts">`
